name: Gold generator
description: Generates gold and ressources for you.

name: Tower freeze
description: Makes enemy's towers not to shoot you.

name: Auto base builder & saver
description: Makes you be able to record bases, and to be able to build them later.

name: Server scanner
description: Scans all servers on zombs.io, and returns people that matched options of score, wave, and name.

name: Auto raid
description: Builds a random base, auto respawns you, enables speed, and buys spear. Perfect for raiding.

name: Base finder
description: Finds any base in your server, and shows them on your mini-map.

name: Clone maker
description: Generates clones that you can control, by clicking a button.

name: Server filler
description: Fills your server, without extra tabs.

name: All servers chat
description: Sends a message on all non-full servers.
